install_msg:
Thanks for installing my Cog!

 This cog requires you to have an api key you can apply for it at <https://forms.gle/TEZ3YbbMPMEWYuuMA>.

 You can then set the amari api key with the `[p]set api amari auth,<api key>` command 
 
 For any feature requests/ suggestions/ bugs, feel free to shoot me a dm at Honkertonken#9221 (694835810347909161)
